{"contents":[{"data":{"text":"A ba","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556418},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556419},{"data":{"text":"这是你离开的第17天","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556420},{"data":{"text":"你是平安夜离开的，连你最后一面我都没见到，甚至你走的那天他们都瞒着我我还愚蠢的以为很多亲戚来仅仅是因为去医院看你。圣诞节那天早上我还在刷着微博给妈妈打电话的时候她强装镇定的声音我都以为是旁边有人她才那样说话。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556422},{"data":{"text":"25下午，妈妈给我打来电话让我回家，到家之后舅舅开车带我走，我问他去哪他说去看看你爸，那时候我才隐隐约约预料到了，我问他你怎么样了，他没有告诉我只是不断跟我说，你要坚强。一路上我没有任何感觉只是一直不自觉的看着窗外。车开到了殡仪馆。一下车我就感觉自己支撑不住了眼泪一下掉了下来，我没有撕心裂肺的哭。有人扶着我走到你的守灵堂前我一下就没了任何眼泪，跪在你堂前，我听见旁边有女人说这就是大悲无泪。但我没有感觉到丝毫悲伤，没有丝毫感觉。后来有人把我扶起我看见妈在一旁哭我只是觉得很假。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556424},{"data":{"text":"第二天下午要下葬了，领魂人打开了棺材，我看见你面带微笑的躺在那里，旁边有人告诉我你应该哭，你要哭给别人看，只是我真的哭不出来只是怔怔的看着母亲在众人安慰下哭得撕心裂肺。最后你穿着滑稽的衣服戴着滑稽的帽子被推进炼灰室，我还是意识不过来你真的走了。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556426},{"data":{"text":"我还记得我小的时候你是校长，每天早晨我起床去上幼儿园的时候你都还未醒来，晚上我回家的时候你还在饭店应酬。我跟你一直都不亲近，从小到大我看着别人家女儿和父亲那么那么亲近我一直都特别羡慕，我一直觉得你不爱我这么多年唯一能给我安慰的就是在想起我很小的时候你把我举过头顶用胡茬扎我的脸。后来有天看到你新钱包里什么都没放第一个放进入的就是我的照片，我就特别感动特别高兴因为我知道了你是爱我的。你住院之后几天的一个早上妈妈跟我说医生说你这病维持得好顶多十年八年 我一下就哭了，我从不在妈妈面前哭所以我一掉眼泪她就愣了，然后说骗我呢。那时候我也不知道她是在骗我还是真的，现在想起来的确是真的，只是不是说十年八年吗？怎么人一下子就没了。其实你住院了之后我关上屋子哭了几回从没在妈妈面前掉过眼泪。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556428},{"data":{"text":"我一直在想你走前有想到我吗，十二月初的时候你还给我做了放糖八宝粥我不喜欢喝但还是喝了一大碗告诉你好喝以后还要喝，上个月你还坐在沙发前面的小凳子上看凤凰卫视，每个礼拜我的衣服你都洗。 从25号下午到现在我都出奇的冷静只是害怕想到你死前也许都没想起我这个姑娘。我还是意识不到你走了，你说的话我还没认真听，你年轻时候的光荣事迹还没给我讲你，年轻时候那么帅画画和书法都那么漂亮，你一直都是我心里最英雄的人我还没告诉你，我一直都那么那么崇拜你我从没说过，我还从未拥抱过你从未对你说我爱你你还从未吃过我做的饭还没等到我去挣钱养你的年纪你就这么没了。我多希望你不要离开，如果真的离开让我跟你好好告别一下也好，别让我抱那么多遗憾，别让我还没来得及做能对你好的事就离开。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556431},{"data":{"text":"你走之后我越来越相信人死之后会有灵魂尚在，有风把我头发吹乱时候我总相信是你在我身边。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556434},{"data":{"text":"现在想起前几年无病呻吟张口闭口说失去说难过说悲伤说失去，真的可笑至极，什么叫失去。如今真的体会到唐山大地震里说，没了，才知道什么叫 没了。世界上唯一一个会真心对我不求回报的男人。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556436},{"data":{"text":"A Ba,我才十七岁，我还有未来七十年要走，我不怕现在没有你教我怎样领会人生怎样为人处事我不怕过得辛苦，我怕只怕我未来那么长我会忘了你我不想时间抹平一切我只想难过越来越深越来越刻骨铭心让我永远不会忘记。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556439},{"data":{"text":"Mogwai的cody 你离开的这些日子我一直日日夜夜听","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556442},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10690227},{"data":{"text":"Of all I knew","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556443},{"data":{"text":"I held too few","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556444},{"data":{"text":"And would you stop me?","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556445},{"data":{"text":"If I tried to stop you?","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556446},{"data":{"text":"Old songs, stay to the end","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556447},{"data":{"text":"I tried a hundred timesAnd","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556448},{"data":{"text":"Sad songs, remind me of friends","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556449},{"data":{"text":"And the way it is, I could leave it all","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556450},{"data":{"text":"And I ask myself, would you care at all","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556451},{"data":{"text":"Old songs, stay to the end","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556452},{"data":{"text":"Sad songs, remind me of friends","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556453},{"data":{"text":"And the way it is, I could leave it all","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556454},{"data":{"text":"And I ask myself, would you care at all","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556455},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10690228},{"data":{"text":"A Ba，我只是很想被你珍惜","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556456},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556467},{"data":{"text":"来自 被豌豆汤喝掉","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":true,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10667239},{"data":{"text":"“爸爸非常有才华，受他影响从小喜欢美术，现在是美术生。有时候讲点故事给自己听。爸爸跟我说过做个有趣的人远比做个事业有成的人难得多。想去金三角那里做个象夫拯救被毒贩扣押来运送毒品的大象。 ”","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":true,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10556457}],"title":"A Ba ,"}